Package ch.ecma.csta.errors Description

This package contains classes that directly map to the CSTA Diagnostic Error Definitions. The primary class is CstaException. The direct children of CstaException represent the different Error Categories also specified. Please see CSTA-269 Section 9.3 for more information about the different Errors.
